title: Girls soccer: Spackenkill beats Rhinebeck in MHAL prelude
text: Girls soccer: Spackenkill beats Rhinebeck in MHAL prelude A.J. Martelli, Poughkeepsie Journal 7:59 p.m. EDT October 14, 2015 Spackenkill's Eileen Fiore and Rhinebeck's Barr Lavi-Romer collide during Wednesday's game in Rhinebeck. Patrick Oehler/Poughkeepsie Journal Spackenkill's Lexie Close jumps up to trap the ball in front of Rhinebeck's Samantha McClenahan during Wednesday's game in Rhinebeck. Patrick Oehler/Poughkeepsie Journal Spackenkill's Katherine Lillis keeps control of the ball ahead of Rhinebeck's Natalie Hutchins during Wednesday's game in Rhinebeck. Patrick Oehler/Poughkeepsie Journal Spackenkill's goalie, Savannah Barefoot grabs the ball away from Rhinebeck's Stephanie Cassens during Wednesday's game in Rhinebeck.
